  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Homage to all (and old) keyboard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An homage to all the old basketball 2D classics!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But, with new mechanics!!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 on 1 streetball matches!!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full control over each layup step, dunk or shoot. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with three different player or style. Choose between shooter, blocker or dunker!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each player has more that 100 signature moves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2D, hand drawn, fluid graphics!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Very competitive and great fun for two players! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot, dunk and block - you will feel!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
